data.description: Introducing an affordable ranch style home. This home is perfect for those tired of renting and ready for a home. This charming property boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths and has lake access to all SPORTS RUSH LAKE and a beach area. All appliances stay with the home. Fenced in backyard. Great location to shopping, restaurants and the Lakeland Trail. Say goodbye to renting and hello to your new lakeside retreat.
